<unit id="52e4092f-1364-4a52-83a5-9c39b1decc1e">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 6</note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>This add-on provides additional touchscreen gestures for NVDA. It also provides a set of gestures for easier browse mode navigation.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="78ed8620-3f8a-4a6f-b362-d349ec3f2c84">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 8</note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Note: this add-on requires NVDA 2025.3.3 or later running on a touchscreen computer with Windows 10 or 11.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
